com.google.android.exoplayer.text.eia608

Class Eia608Parser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.android.exoplayer.text.eia608.Eia608Parser

  • public final class Eia608Parser
extends java.lang.Object
    Facilitates the extraction and parsing of EIA-608 (a.k.a. "line 21 captions" and "CEA-608") Closed Captions from the SEI data block from H.264.

      • isSeiMessageEia608

        public static boolean isSeiMessageEia608(int payloadType,
                                         int payloadLength,
                                         ParsableByteArray payload)
        Inspects an sei message to determine whether it contains EIA-608.

        The position of payload is left unchanged.

        Parameters:
        payloadType - The payload type of the message.
        payloadLength - The length of the payload.
        payload - A ParsableByteArray containing the payload.
        Returns:
        True if the sei message contains EIA-608. False otherwise.
